data.description: HUGE PRICE Improvement and Great Opportunity for LOAN assumption at 3.75%. Welcome to 8613 Port Sudan Ct, a magnificent property that embodies the pinnacle of luxury living. Located in a beautiful neighborhood, this home offers an unparalleled opportunity to experience elegance, comfort, and modern sophistication. This comfortable property features an incredible private annex with its own laundry and kitchen, providing independence to the tenant from the owners, which can be rented for the amount of $1,200. Situated in a prime location, you'll enjoy easy access to schools, shopping centers, parks, and major roadways. This is more than a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade. Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to make 8613 Port Sudan Ct your forever home. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and immerse yourself in the luxury and comfort that this property offers. Your dream home awaits – seize it today!
